        </summary>
        <div class="px-6 pb-4 text-sm text-gray-600">Any MCP-compatible AI client: Claude Code, Cline, Roo Code, Cursor, Windsurf, and more. The web UI works in any browser. The OOS format is platform-agnostic. Claude, GPT, Gemini, open-source models -- it does not matter which AI you use.</div>
      </details>

